				<outline text="&quot;You can see the smoke&quot;" type="outline">
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.metafilter.com/detail.cfm?link_ID=1648&quot;&gt;On MetaFilter&lt;/a&gt;, I posted a note on Array's return (there was an earlier thread about Array's disappearance), noting that Garret was covering the fires in New Mexico. "/>
					<outline text="&quot;Eventually the electronic flames ran out of energy, and in an amazing case of synchronicity, the flames showed up in the forests of New Mexico.&quot;"/>
					<outline text="A reporter from the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lobolink.com/&quot;&gt;New Mexico Daily Lobo&lt;/a&gt; posted links to their work. &quot;I live in Albuquerque and you can see the smoke from the Interstate. It's surreal.&quot; "/>
					<outline text="&lt;i&gt;This is the Web I work for. A human network covering the world. &lt;/i&gt;"/>
					</outline>
